    "TitleKey": "Intersec_TSG_BombRun_Solo_Title_001",
    "Description": "MISSION SPECS\n\nArea of Operation: Nyx System \nHostile Forces: Shattered Blade\nEquipment Specs: Combat Ships w/Ordnance\nBriefing: \nLocal assets have indicated that Shattered Blade elements are attempting to rebuild one of their stations and Intersec is looking for a pilot to make sure that doesn't happen.\n\nThey've managed to get basic turret defenses back online but currently only have <EM4>two power relays activated</EM4>. These will be your targets as they <EM4>cannot be destroyed by energy weapons, you will need to bring ballistic or ordnance to be effective</EM4>. \n\nReactivation of this station will allow the Shattered Blade to try and reclaim a foothold in this system and we can't let that happen.\n\nGood luck,   \n\nDeacon Tobin \nOperations Manager \nInterSec Defense Solutions  \n\nThis communication consists of confidential information solely intended for the recipient. Please disregard if received in error and notify the sender. All operations are conducted at the contractor\u2019s own personal risk and must adhere to UEE and system law where applicable.",
